node.text:
You have two choices when starting a business and running a business.. You can choose to be the next Blockbuster and not changing with the times. Or you can find the need of your business and chose to become the next Netflix.

The reality is, without social media for your new idea, business model, start-up, etc.. In the next ten years, you will become extinct just like Blockbuster.

I will teach you everything I know when mentoring you to become your version of the next Netflix through social media. You are one cIick away from having a proven blueprint to starting that million-dollar idea you have using social media.

I'm only taking 100 more go-getters this week for my complimentary training. View my bio.

GO TO SPECTACULARMASTERCLASS.COM

Drop a💰if you ready make the biggest bag of your life this year!

node.text:
What happens if you’re on a highway looking at the other lanes all the time?  You gonna get in an accident.

So when you drive in your lane in life, stay focused and you’ll get to your destination in no time by following a proven roadmap to success. 

Say AMEN if you’re staying focused

node.text:
Waiting for luck to fix your problems causes new problems, because no one ever made it from waiting around at home wishing.

You can visualize your success all your life but you never do anything about it- it's just dreaming. Take action and follow your dreams no matter what. For every word you say, you could take 2 actions and get it done.

Comment 🔥 if you agree

node.text:
For every failure in life, there is a lesson.

For every success person, there is a mentor.

For every circle, someone is out growing it.

For every human, there is a God giving talent and purpose.

To become the best, you must learn from the best.

Go to MentorMeSpec.com to join my apprentice program. I’m discounting the program for the next 24 hours for the first 100 people — before the price goes back up. 🖤

node.text:
There's no point trying to become successful on your own. Trying to figure everything out by yourself and struggling by yourself. When someone has already made the mistakes you’re about to make, lost the money that you are about to lose. Learn from someone that has already been where you want to be in life. 

There is no lack of information, it’s only a lack of Accountability and guidance. When you are ready, God will put the right person in front of you but it’s up to you to take advantage of the opportunity.

You only get two life-changing opportunities in a lifetime. Make sure when they present themselves, you take that leap of faith.

Tag someone that needs to hear this message!

node.text:
If you can figure out how to get attention with putting your message in front of the right audience... You will never go hungry another day in your life.

The best skill to master is social media. Those who understand will dominate now and in the future. Those who don’t — business will die and become the next blockbuster story for not keeping up with the new ways of doing things.

The person with the most attention on social media wins in any industry. Don’t try to figure this out by yourself, find the proven model and execute on it step by step.

What was your biggest takeaway?

node.text:
I want you to focus on what matters the most. RIGHT NOW. Not the past. Not blaming your parents, spouse, previous traumas, etc.. To have the life you have always dreamed of will happen when you let go, forgive, and heal.

There’s a lesson to be learned in every tragedy. It’s not about what happens but more about how you respond to what happens.

I have trained myself to have a growth mindset and think of every situation as a cup half full and not half empty. When you go into situations, your first thought should not be “what’s the worst that can happen” but more of “what’s the best that can happen” but with knowing the worst.

Take risk, invest in yourself and think about what can go right instead of what can go wrong. Not what you will lose by investing but what you will lose by NOT investing.

Say AMEN if you agree! And why? Let me know your thoughts

You have two choices when starting a business and running a business.. You can choose to be the next Blockbuster and not changing with the times. Or you can find the need of your business and chose to become the next Netflix.

The reality is, without social media for your new idea, business model, start-up, etc.. In the next ten years, you will become extinct just like Blockbuster.

I will teach you everything I know when mentoring you to become your version of the next Netflix through social media. You are one cIick away from having a proven blueprint to starting that million-dollar idea you have using social media.

I'm only taking 100 more go-getters this week for my complimentary training. View my bio.

node.text:
@ThePowerCircleGlobal shines a light through the darkness, helping to bring out the leader that exists within all of us. Not everyone is ready to reach their next level – it takes a certain transparency, grit and self-accountability that many shy away from. If, however, you’re ready and willing to take the necessary steps to expand your life, the Power of Branding by The Power Circle welcomes you warmly into the inner circle. ⁣
⁣
• This 1 day virtual event will take place from June 27th, with invaluable advice, lessons and blueprints from a roster of 9 esteemed speakers.⁣
⁣
•  Power of branding, systems, advertising and personal development education in a virtual setting⁣
⁣
• Are you eager to learn how to turn this economic downturn into your secret weapon?⁣
⁣
• Are you interested in learning how the world’s top entrepreneurs pivot during times like this?⁣
⁣
• Do you want the keys to staying calm in a crisis?⁣
⁣
• Are you thinking of launching a business or opening a store?⁣
⁣
• Are you a content creator or independent contractor struggling to build your audience or expand engagement?⁣
⁣
• Do you simply wish to mix and mingle with more professionals in your field?⁣
⁣
• The Power of Branding virtual event has assembled an all-star list of speakers. The 9 speakers range from ecommerce and financial experts to real estate professionals, investors and more. Each speaker will lead a 30 mins to one hour virtual workshop where viewers will get the chance to ask specific questions and talk with our experts and each other in real-time. Go to register at www.ThePowerCircle.live and follow @thepowercircleglobal to stay plugged in.⁣

@stevecanal @ceomattyj @sleepis4suckers @liabdias @christiannahurt @dr.omaikofi @kendrastephen @michelvalbrun @tinabonnerlive @thepowercircleglobal
⁣
#ThePowerOf #MotivatedMindset #ThePowerCircle #ThePowerOfSeries

node.text:
Waiting for luck to fix your problems causes new problems, because no one ever made it from waiting around at home wishing.

You can visualize your success all your life but you never do anything about it- it's just dreaming. Take action and follow your dreams no matter what. For every word you say, you could take 2 actions and get it done.

Comment 🔥 if you agree

The last thing you want to do is guess what’s your next move to be wealthy and financially free. It’s hard, frustrating, and confusing..

I been there, done that.

But then I realized I needed to focus on the WHO and not the WHAT. Not what I had to do to become successful, but who did I have to model after and have coach me that would get me to where I desire to be at a accelerated pace.

By the way. Which slide do you like?

Names:
Slide 1. Powerful
Slide 2. Successful
Slide 3. Wealthy
Slide 4. Servant

Drop your pick below
